======
Intro
======
"get_glite_job_attrs.py" parses various logging information available in gUse and the gLite WMS to provide as much as possible the information of the grid job generated by the workflow execution. It serves as a tool for debugging workflow execution down to the job level and for collecting job-related attributs for the workflow provenance.

