        `-- python
            |-- elementtree
            `-- mysql
======
requirement
======
- Python 2.4+
- simplejson python module: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/simplejson

======
Usage
======
usage: 

  get_glite_job_attrs.py [options] WFNAME_1 WFNAME_2 ...

example:

  get_glite_job_attrs.py [-v|--verbose] Freesurfer_V5_NSG_1792_2013-10-15-154837

options:
  --version             show program's version number and exit
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -v VERBOSE, --vebose=VERBOSE
                        set one of the following verbosity levels. -1:ERROR,
                        0|default:WARNING, 1:INFO, 2:DEBUG
  -c FCONFIG, --config=FCONFIG
                        set the configuration parameters, see "config.ini"
  -f FORMAT, --format=FORMAT
                        set output format
  -p, --provenance      set to run over workflows in the provenance database
                        and fill in job attributes
